qnote (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release (Closes: #XXXXXX)
  * Features:
    - Note management with Markdown support
    - Code snippet storage with syntax highlighting
    - TODO tracking with priorities and due dates
    - Tag-based organization system
    - Full-text search functionality
    - External editor integration
    - Rich terminal UI
    - SQLite database backend
    - Shell completion (bash, zsh, fish) - auto-installed
    - Configuration management (qnote config commands)
    - Comprehensive documentation

